Package com.nandox.jop.core.processor

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PageExpression
    Represent generic page expression.
    An expression is java (or other) language expression used in page into html attribute or jbean tag
    PageWriteExpression
    Represent write page expression.
    An expression that can also manage a value to write in some bean
    RefreshableBlock
    Represent a page block refreshable when related monitored bean change
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractPageExpression<E>
    Abstract implementation for page expression
    BooleanPageExpression
    Boolean returned Expression Page: used for boolean page block attributes
    CollectionPageExpression
    Page expression that return a data collection.
    The collection can be an native array or some implementation of java Collection
    JopId
    Class that represents an Jop Identifier
    PageApp
    Class of Page application.
    One page application is composite by PageBlock, every block can contains PageExpression
    PageBlock  
    SimplePageExpression
    Simple page expression that return a string format
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DomException
    DOM exception thrown in case of syntax error
    ParseException
    Parse exception thrown in case of syntax error
